# Transient per-run artifact dirs (screenshots, PDFs, archives, heap snapshots,
# videos, HARs) the file-io tools write under a workspace-* temp dir. The
# report-<stamp>.{json,md} + FULL-REPORT.md ARE tracked (the deliverable).
workspace-*/

# Machine reports are reproducible (`pnpm --filter @browxai/capability-testbed
# report`) and large (~1.4 MB JSON). The curated FULL-REPORT.md IS tracked.
report-*.json
report-*.md
